s/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c105c14d11adec818f6c47444bdc44dad081730","tid":482522,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"講到尾 <br />\n&quot;自己都唔信&quot; 同 &quot;驚訝&quot; 個位喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}